{"word":"χασμάω","slug":"χασμάω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>χασμάω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:χάσμα'><el>χάσμα</el></a>\n<el>(χασμάω,) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to yawn, gape wide</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>as <a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <el>χασμάομαι</el>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}